trans-unit.source: The MsmqIntegrationBinding class maps Microsoft Message Queuing (MSMQ) messages to [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] messages.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MsmqIntegrationBinding tilordner Microsoft Message Queuing (MSMQ) meldinger til [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] meldinger.

trans-unit.source: This binding can be used to enable [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] applications to send and receive messages to and from existing MSMQ applications that use COM, native C++ APIs or the types defined in the <xref:System.Messaging> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Denne bindingen, kan brukes til å aktivere [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programmer for å sende og motta meldinger til og fra eksisterende MSMQ-programmer som bruker COM, opprinnelig C++ APIs eller typene som er definert i den <xref:System.Messaging>navneområde.</xref:System.Messaging>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"></xref> class by using the specified <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method enables you to instantiate a new instance of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding> and pass in a security mode.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig å starte en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding>og sende i en sikkerhetsmodus.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding>

trans-unit.source: The security mode supported by the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel
trans-unit.target: Sikkerhetsmodusen støttes av kanalen for Message Queuing (MSMQ)-integrering

trans-unit.source: The value is not within the range of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er ikke innenfor området med <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"></xref> class from the settings of a specified configuration binding element.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationBinding"> </xref> klassen fra innstillingene til en angitt konfigurasjonselementet binding.

trans-unit.source: This method allows you to place the binding settings in a configuration file but add the actual binding in code.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan du plassere bindingsinnstillingene i en konfigurasjonsfil, men legge til den faktiske bindingen i koden.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_configurationName" name="configurationName" href=""></xref> attribute that identifies the <xref uid="langword_csharp_binding" name="binding" href=""></xref> element whose settings are used to initialize the binding.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_configurationName" name="configurationName" href=""> </xref> attributt som identifiserer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_binding" name="binding" href=""> </xref> elementet med innstillinger som brukes til å initialisere bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns the binding elements in the basic profile stack.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer bindingen-elementer i den grunnleggende profil bunken.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection> that contains the stack of binding elements in the basic profile stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection>som inneholder stakken for binding elementer i den grunnleggende profil bunken.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity"></xref> that is associated with this binding.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity"> </xref> som er knyttet til denne bindingen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity> encapsulates Message Queuing (MSMQ) transport security settings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity>innkapsler transport sikkerhetsinnstillinger for Message Queuing (MSMQ).</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity"></xref> that is associated with this binding.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurity"> </xref> som er knyttet til denne bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the serialization format to be used to serialize or deserialize the message.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir serialiseringsformatet som skal brukes til å serialisere eller deserialisere meldingen.

trans-unit.source: This property returns an enumeration value that specifies how a [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] message will be serialized and deserialized.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer en opplistingsverdi som angir hvordan en [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] meldingen serialisert og deserialiseres.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"></xref> object that represents the type of serialization to use.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"> </xref> objektet som representerer typen serialisering skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that specifies whether security information should be serialized.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om sikkerhetsinformasjon skal serialiseres.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if security information should be serialized; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis sikkerhetsinformasjon skal serialiseres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
